headline.main: After Bombs, Pakistan Tightens Security for Rare Major Cricket Match
headline.print_headline: After Bombs, Pakistan Tightens Security for Rare Major Cricket Match

lead_paragraph: China has cut its growth target this year as the world's second-largest economy pushes through painful reforms to address a rapid build-up in debt, and erects a "firewall" against financial risks.
